 《哈利·波特》主演鲁珀特·格林特在税务纠纷中败诉后被勒令支付 180 万英镑https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-star-rupert-grint-ordered-to-pay-1-8m-after-losing-tax-dispute-3817347?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=哈利波特明星鲁珀特格林特被命令在输税纠纷后支付 1-8mChris Edwards Fri, 29 Nov 2024 22:00:44 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3817347 <p><img width="2158" height="1398" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08.jpg 2158w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-400x259.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-800x518.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-696x451.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-1392x902.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-1068x692.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2158px) 100vw, 2158px" /></p><p>英国税务海关总署的一项调查对他的一份纳税申报表提出了异议</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-star-rupert-grint-ordered-to-pay-1-8m-after-losing-tax-dispute-3817347">《哈利·波特》主演鲁珀特·格林特在税务纠纷败诉后被勒令支付 180 万英镑，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2158" height="1398" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08.jpg 2158w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-400x259.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-800x518.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-696x451.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-1392x902.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-31-at-15.54.08-1068x692.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2158px) 100vw, 2158px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/harry-potter"><em>《哈利·波特》</em></a>主演鲁珀特·格林特在与英国税务海关总署的法律纠纷中败诉后，被勒令缴纳 180 万英镑税款。</p><p>这位在所有八部电影中饰演罗恩·韦斯莱的演员最初被要求在 2019 年支付这笔款项，因为英国税务海关总署 (HMRC) 的调查对他的一份纳税申报表提出了异议。</p><p>格林特的律师提出上诉，辩称他从一家公司收到的钱已作为资本资产正确征税，但英国税务海关总署表示，这笔钱应该作为收入按更高的税率征税。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c0rgkkpl0dno" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>报道，格林特的索赔已被税务法庭法官驳回，他现在必须支付总计 180 万英镑的费用。</p><p>在 2011-2012 纳税年度，格林特从一家管理他业务的公司收到了 450 万英镑，他是该公司的唯一股东。这笔款项被描述为“可能是<em>哈利波特</em>电影的剩余收入和奖金”。</p><p>这位演员辩称，他可以按 10% 的税率缴纳资本利得税，而不是按最高 52% 的税率缴纳所得税和国民保险。 </p><figure id="attachment_3530523" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3530523" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3530523" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo.jpg" alt="哈利·波特演员表" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Harry-Potter-cast-photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3530523" class="wp-caption-text">鲁珀特·格林特、艾玛·沃森和丹尼尔·雷德克利夫 图片来源：Anthony Harvey/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在裁决中，法庭法官哈里特·摩根驳回了格林特的上诉，并表示这笔钱“大部分价值都来自格林特先生的活动”，这些钱“以其他方式实现”为收入。</p><p> 2019 年，这位演员在另一起涉及 100 万英镑退税的单独法庭诉讼中败诉。</p><p>在其他新闻中，华纳兄弟最近宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-will-have-longevity-like-batman-with-fans-asking-what-harry-are-you-studio-says-3810320"><em>《哈利·波特》</em>将与《蝙蝠侠》一样长寿</a>，未来几年可能会有多名演员扮演这位名义上的巫师。</p><p>与此同时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-tv-series-will-be-more-in-depth-says-studio-boss-thats-the-whole-reason-were-on-this-journey-3805020">，新的《哈利·波特》衍生系列正在制作中，预计将于 2026 年上映</a>。该剧预计播出七季，每一季都会改编<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-k-rowling">JK 罗琳</a>系列中的一本书。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-star-rupert-grint-ordered-to-pay-1-8m-after-losing-tax-dispute-3817347">《哈利·波特》主演鲁珀特·格林特在税务纠纷败诉后被勒令支付 180 万英镑，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
